  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/58e9899f37fcbff57ccd50a1e2b14ca7.avif?t=1667030671\" width=596 height=326 /></span>.<br>Lazerhawk is a racing game inspired by the visuals, music, games and cars from the late 80s and early 90s. It's built on a custom game engine,<br>with an authentic retro feel and unique graphics. you will first start with one car, then you will be able to upgrade it or buy other cars with the money<br>earned at the end of each run.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/a9dd98260b8aa61cf0645f328fe6fc5b.poster.avif?t=1667030671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/a9dd98260b8aa61cf0645f328fe6fc5b.webm?t=1667030671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/a9dd98260b8aa61cf0645f328fe6fc5b.mp4?t=1667030671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br>Race your car through different unique level!<br>Watch out for other vehicles on the road. playing this game it is a challenging and exciting experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/e89cb3a6b90b4eebf2ae44034656c4ab.poster.avif?t=1667030671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/e89cb3a6b90b4eebf2ae44034656c4ab.webm?t=1667030671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/e89cb3a6b90b4eebf2ae44034656c4ab.mp4?t=1667030671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>Features:<br><br>■ No less than 8 cars .<br>■ More than 3 different level .<br>■ 4 different game modes .<br>■ Proper score system .<br>■ Purchase system of car performance upgrades .<br>■ Purchase system of new colors and wheels .<br>■ Endless Highway .",
